Please run through the steps below to play with the project
- Import project into an IDE, for example IntelliJ IDEA
- Open the terminal to root directory of the project
- Run command docker-compose up to start the Kafka server (Must install docker-compose in the machine first)
- Start the project from Main object
- Use the attached postman collection to call two provided APIs (Import collection Json file to Postman first)
Enjoy!!!

*** Please be aware that the order of dateTime field in request body of adding bitcoin amount API is matter, you must sequentially call
this API with ascendant time.
For example
{
    "amount": 1.1,
    "dateTime": "2022-02-05T20:00:00+00:00"
}
{
    "amount": 1.1,
    "dateTime": "2022-02-05T20:01:00+00:00"
}
These must be in order.
